      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "sometimes i sit here staring at my monitor for hours after i finish work and it just hits me how quiet everything is. like, i go through my whole day, i send emails, i do my tasks, i exist... but if i just stopped, if i just stopped showing up or replying or being \"online,\" would the world even flicker? would anyone actually notice i was gone or would it just stay this same empty silence?",
      "beast_suffix": "",
      "targeted_response_start_logprob": 0.0
    },
